  | \__\\\ \            . R E L E A S E   N O T E S .               / ///__/ | 
  |                                                                          | 
  |      The adventure takes place in a fantasy world filled with beautiful  |
  |      cinematic graphics and vibrant characters. It includes more than    |
  |      50 hours of gameplay and is the only next-gen RPG with the          |
  |      fast-action SpeedTactics Battle System, which enables the player    |
  |      to move his or her characters and use distance-dependent attacks    |
  |      while in battle.                                                    |
  |                                                                          |
  |      In Enchanted Arms, players will embark on an epic RPG adventure and |
  |      escape to a fantasy world filled with unique and bizarre creatures. |
  |      Taking the role of Atsuma, enchanter-in-training, players will      |
  |      transform from a na∩ve student into the most powerful savior in a   |
  |      war 1,000 years in the making. In an immersive, deep storyline      |
  |      filled with increasingly difficult challenges, players will meet    |
  |      new allies and master Atsuma's special fighting and magic           |
  |      abilities.                                                          |
